  <brief_title>Blood Loss During Cesarean Section. Comparing Two Techniques of Blunt Expansion of Uterine Incision: Transversal vs. Cephalad-caudad,</brief_title>
  <official_title>Blood Loss During Cesarean Section. Comparing Two Techniques of Blunt Expansion of Uterine Incision: Transversal vs. Cephalad-caudad. A Randomized, Controlled Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
